---
import MoveRight from "@assets/svg/move-right.svg";
import Phone from "@assets/svg/phone.svg";

---

<section class="bg-neutral-200 py-20 border-b border-b-neutral-600">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-neutral-900 font-bold">
            ¿Listo para transformar tu proyecto en realidad?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-900 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Nuestro compromiso es construir de manera responsable, apostando por la  calidad, innovación y la sostenibilidad.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4">
            <a
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-neutral-900 hover:bg-black text-white font-semibold px-6 py-2 transition-all whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 cursor-pointer group [&_svg]:size-4 [&_svg]:shrink-0"
                href="/contacto/"
                >Solicitar Presupuesto
                <MoveRight class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
            </a>
            <a
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white hover:bg-primary-500 hover:text-white text-neutral-900 font-semibold px-6 py-2 transition-all whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 cursor-pointer [&_svg]:size-4 [&_svg]:shrink-0"
                href="tel:925090798">Llamar Ahora
                <Phone />
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
